name: Cafe Food Planet

reviews.review_text: Really nice location to relax at near the beach, eat tasty food and enjoy the sunset. Everything is clean and the service is normal but after ordering hard to catch waiter later. The food was also tasty. The price is also acceptable. There are a lot of dogs as well but they aren’t that annoying. There are also many locals walking around and selling various items and coconuts. The beach itself is also pretty clean.
Good vibes and decent service. Food is good and prepared neatly. No loud music and great vibes.

This place is a hidden gem. It is situated in between Morjim and Arambol beach . The Restraunt is a bit pricey as here most of the foreign tourists stay to see the beautiful sunset of Goa. Food is good but the service is not too good as all their staffs are busy and  not paying attention. We ordered a tea and juice. Juice arrived fast but tea never arrived and at the time of payment they were giving it at reception. I understand it is not error of anyone but it happens sometimes at busy time of Restraunt . I just suggest to increase staff if you have a lot of work.

description:
**Café Food Planet: A Hidden Gem Along the Shores of Mandrem**

Nestled along the serene beaches of Mandrem, Café Food Planet boasts an impressive rating of 4.3, with a substantial 1,545 reviews highlighting its captivating blend of culinary delights and breathtaking sunsets. Customers frequently tag their experiences with words like "beach" (158 mentions), "shack" (47), and "sunset" (41), which emphasizes the restaurant's scenic location and relaxed vibe that make it a perfect retreat for both tourists and locals alike.

**Ambiance & Design**

As you step into Café Food Planet, you are instantly greeted by the refreshing ocean breeze, the sound of gentle waves, and an inviting beachfront atmosphere. The café features rustic wood furniture and vibrant decor that beautifully captures the essence of a beach shack. The tasteful decorations and warm lighting create a cozy environment that feels like a home away from home. Photos reveal picturesque views from the terrace, allowing diners to soak in stunning sunsets that meld into the horizon, making the dining experience all the more memorable.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

Café Food Planet offers a diverse menu that's well-prepared and known for its vibrant flavors. Signature dishes that stand out include a variety of freshly prepared seafood options, refreshing juices, and comfort food tailored to both local and international palates. Reviewers appreciate the meticulous presentation of dishes, which are not only flavorful but also visually appealing. While the café is described as slightly pricier than typical local eateries, this is attributed to its location, often frequented by foreign tourists seeking that perfect Goan sunset moment. The reviews also suggest a commitment to cleanliness and quality, aligning with its beachside charm.

**Customer Experience & Service**

The service at Café Food Planet receives mixed feedback; while guests express appreciation for the good vibes and decent overall service, some reviews highlight lapses in attentiveness during peak hours. A common sentiment suggests that the staff could benefit from a few additional hands during busy times to ensure all guests feel fully attended to. Despite the occasional delays—such as drinks arriving separately from food—reviewers maintain that the atmosphere remains relaxed and enjoyable, with friendly interactions generally reported. The presence of wandering locals selling coconuts adds to the authentic beach experience, although patrons are advised to be prepared for these incidental encounters.

**Popularity & Reviews**

Café Food Planet is often described as a hidden gem between Morjim and Arambol beach, making it a sought-after spot for those seeking an authentic Goan experience with a side of tranquility. The establishment garners significant social media buzz as visitors share their picturesque meals against stunning backdrops of seaside sunsets. While there are no specific critic ratings or notable visits cited, the sheer volume of positive reviews reflects its emerging reputation as a must-visit destination for both food lovers and sunset chasers alike.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

The allure of Café Food Planet is beautifully captured in images shared by customers. From the vibrant plates of food that highlight the café's commitment to quality to the breathtaking sunset views that invite patrons to linger just a little longer, each photo paints an inviting picture of what one can expect when visiting. The captured ambiance of diners enjoying their meals against the backdrop of the setting sun reinforces why this café has captured the hearts of so many.

In conclusion, Café Food Planet offers not merely a meal but an experience steeped in flavor, local culture, and scenic beauty—making it a treasured spot for anyone looking to unwind by the beach while enjoying delicious food. Whether you're a local or just passing through, this café promises to be a delightful addition to your culinary journey in Goa.
